<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ECONOMIST-BUDGET </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
   (These excellent ``separate-buy'' articles are from the current
(week beginning 15 January 2000) ECONOMIST magazine.)  
  
