Warner Music: because AOL knows its subscribers, they will be clips
of the kind of music those individuals might want to listen to. &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; (END OF SECOND OPTIONAL TRIM. STORY CONTINUES TO 1,200) &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   This merger, then, brings forward the shift to narrowcasting.
Some people fear the social consequences.
</P>
<P>
   In an age when the bonds of family and community are loosening,
