<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-18 13:55 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9118 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r d BC-ROSE-PISTOLA-LADN 2takes &LR;    01-18 0805
