<P>
   GORE-IOWA (Indianola, Iowa) _ Just after his final debate with
rival former Sen. Bill Bradley, Vice President Al Gore plunges into
a day of campaigning in Iowa, far ahead in the polls leading up to
Monday's delegate-selection.
</P>
