<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-18 17:27 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9332 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i BC-GERMANY-SCANDAL-800(2     01-18 0840
