<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-18 21:52 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9640 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k BC-DOWD-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      01-18 0710
