<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-01-18 22:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9679 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-GM-ROBERTS-NYT &LR;      01-18 0773
